# libgost-engine: loaded lazily at runtime, only when the verified chain
# contains GOST-signed certs. Pure RSA deployments do not need it; on
# Astra hosts the package is named libgost-astra.
# libudev1 / libdbus-1-3 / libsystemd0: pulled in automatically by
# ${shlibs:Depends} from the binary's NEEDED entries when the daemon
# subcommand is built.
# polkitd: not invoked from the PAM module or daemon today, kept as
# Suggests for future cert-management UI integration.
# libpdp3 / libparsec-base3: required at runtime only when the binary is
# built with the `astra-mac` feature; on non-Astra hosts (Debian/Ubuntu)
# the package functions as a stub (postinst skips МКЦ setup). Both stay
# as Recommends so apt on Astra still pulls them in, while standard
# Debian/Ubuntu installs do not fail on a missing package. For an
# Astra-specific deb build, promote these to hard Depends in the Astra
# build script. `libparsec-base3` carries `parsec_capget` (verified on
# Astra CI 2026-05-15, run 25903325006) — without it the astra-mac build
# fails to link with `undefined symbol: parsec_capget`.
Recommends:
 libgost-engine | gost-engine | libgost-astra,
 libpkcs11-helper1,
 librtpkcs11ecp,
 libpdp3 (>= 3.11+ci97~),
 libparsec-base3 (>= 3.11+ci97~)
Suggests:
 opensc,
 p11-kit,
 pamtester,
 polkitd | policykit-1
Description: USB-token PKI authentication PAM module for Astra Linux SE
 Tessera authenticates a local UNIX user by verifying a certificate
 stored on a removable USB token (PKCS#12 file or PKCS#11 device such as
 Rutoken / JaCarta). Russian GOST cryptography is supported via the
 system-installed gost-engine OpenSSL provider.
 .
 The package ships:
   * /lib/security/pam_tessera.so  - the PAM module
   * /usr/bin/tessera - userspace CLI (daemon subcommand handles udev/D-Bus)
     events, OCSP/CRL caching, and inter-session screen-lock hooks
   * Example configuration under /etc/tessera/
   * A drop-in PAM stack at /etc/pam.d/tessera
 .
 Designed for Astra Linux SE 1.7+ but builds on Debian 12 / Ubuntu 22.04.
 .
 Russian description:
 .
 PAM-модуль для аутентификации пользователей по сертификату на USB-токене.
 Поддерживаются режимы PKCS#12 (файл с защитой парольной фразой) и PKCS#11
 (Рутокен, JaCarta), включая криптографию ГОСТ через gost-engine. Назначен
 для Astra Linux SE 1.7+, собирается также под Debian 12 и Ubuntu 22.04.
